5d8659f4-321f-4c0f-9d84-dceb9a4b4e5b.title: Clerk
5d8659f4-321f-4c0f-9d84-dceb9a4b4e5b.text:
Hello, welcome to the Civic Office of West Ardougne.
How can I help you?

30f0c4d6-1d2c-4eb9-960e-360bfef015f6.title: Clerk
30f0c4d6-1d2c-4eb9-960e-360bfef015f6.text: The city warder Bravek is in there.

3645cd0a-5f5c-4035-8f1d-25a792815857.title: Clerk
3645cd0a-5f5c-4035-8f1d-25a792815857.text: He has asked not to be disturbed.

bce42584-f903-4d6f-af38-3f2d2df6b321.title: Clerk
bce42584-f903-4d6f-af38-3f2d2df6b321.text:
Hello, welcome to the Civic Office of West Ardougne.
How can I help you?

options.text: I need permission to enter a plague house.

5ead75ba-ab21-49f5-a26c-eaf613b1efb9.title: Clerk
5ead75ba-ab21-49f5-a26c-eaf613b1efb9.text: The city warder Bravek is in there.

61e672b7-ac9d-4c5c-955d-ed60f8400f17.title: Clerk
61e672b7-ac9d-4c5c-955d-ed60f8400f17.text: He has asked not to be disturbed.

options.text: This is urgent though! Someone's been kidnapped!
Do you know when he will be available?

1fac910e-ea53-4798-ba01-9879d853525e.title: <player>
1fac910e-ea53-4798-ba01-9879d853525e.text: Do you know when he will be available?

9eb5909e-69d1-4ace-9fee-47e3a95310fd.title: Clerk
9eb5909e-69d1-4ace-9fee-47e3a95310fd.text: Oh I don't know, an hour or so maybe.

61703bda-6e3e-42d6-9e83-c866aa529657.title: <player>
61703bda-6e3e-42d6-9e83-c866aa529657.text: I need permission to enter a plague house.

425cf050-6783-48ce-ba16-f4e3bf3aa9a4.title: Clerk
425cf050-6783-48ce-ba16-f4e3bf3aa9a4.text:
Rather you than me! The mourners normally deal with
that stuff, you should speak to them. Their headquarters
are right near the city gate.

options.text: Surely you don't let them run everything for you?
This is urgent though! Someone's been kidnapped!

abd8d881-7723-4866-8bad-ba281437bdbd.title: <player>
abd8d881-7723-4866-8bad-ba281437bdbd.text: Surely you don't let them run everything for you?

1a63262a-524f-4e3e-990b-c4e541446d02.title: Clerk
1a63262a-524f-4e3e-990b-c4e541446d02.text:
Well, they do know what they're doing here. If they did
start doing something badly Bravek, the city warder,
would have the power to override them. I can't see that
happening though.

options.text: Can I speak to Bravek anyway?

238edd5e-9a5c-4caf-a2e6-6d47160a2671.title: <player>
238edd5e-9a5c-4caf-a2e6-6d47160a2671.text: Can I speak to Bravek anyway?

5526e57a-637d-44d9-881d-a893497164fe.title: Clerk
5526e57a-637d-44d9-881d-a893497164fe.text: He has asked not to be disturbed.

options.text: This is urgent though! Someone's been kidnapped!
Do you know when he will be available?

5e8ce2cf-9c7a-47ac-920a-d599680f7e34.title: <player>
5e8ce2cf-9c7a-47ac-920a-d599680f7e34.text: This is urgent though! Someone's been kidnapped!

800e6b2c-00b8-4186-a278-31c309cf1763.title: Clerk
800e6b2c-00b8-4186-a278-31c309cf1763.text: I'll see what I can do I suppose.

a1b3f544-9af9-4bd2-bd5a-dfa74b1b0d76.title: Clerk
a1b3f544-9af9-4bd2-bd5a-dfa74b1b0d76.text:
Mr Bravek, there's a man here who really needs to
speak to you.

3bc9b398-12e0-4266-ac61-9f780e351048.title: Bravek
3bc9b398-12e0-4266-ac61-9f780e351048.text: I suppose they can come in then. If they keep it short.

97259a51-1f28-496c-a9c3-e77ccbb04df0.title: Clerk
97259a51-1f28-496c-a9c3-e77ccbb04df0.text:
Hello, welcome to the Civic Office of West Ardougne.
How can I help you?

62176009-f932-4b43-960c-51386110efc9.title: Clerk
62176009-f932-4b43-960c-51386110efc9.text: The city warder Bravek is in there.
